    "is_free": true,
    "description": "加入罗凌竞技场! 和伙伴来一场1v1对决，或者和多达7人的对手角逐，一同争夺命运之冠!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >=卡牌和自走棋的创新结合=</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220730/extras/28fbe227d326396ab355636641ba0eb0.poster.avif?t=1741142009\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220730/extras/28fbe227d326396ab355636641ba0eb0.webm?t=1741142009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220730/extras/28fbe227d326396ab355636641ba0eb0.mp4?t=1741142009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在中世纪奇幻风格的背景下，体验卡牌和自走棋的创新结合。牌尖转动和短兵相接的痛快场景，绝对会让你肾上腺素激增。巧妙制定战略，用一副好牌来争夺象征最高权力的命运之冠，不然就眼睁睁地看着你的黄金被对手夺走。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >=传奇故事背后的中世纪权力斗争=</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220730/extras/754f7c124d14910c36ba52ab88199b02.avif?t=1741142009\" width=616 height=347 /></span><br>扮演数位带有独特配音并个性迥异的中世纪贵族，在象征命运的牌桌上揭开古老的家族历史。在命运多舛的凯撒十五世统治下的动荡时代，最后走出罗凌竞技场的胜利者，将成为凯撒帝国的下一任帝皇，而他/她将直面与飞龙勾结的海盗女皇的威胁。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >=沉浸式的影音体验=</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220730/extras/2b0a09ecd4e8decbed781c16d9adcd20.avif?t=1741142009\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>漫步在大理石柱子环绕的走廊、欣赏奢华的宫殿和宏伟的竞技场，一睹凯撒帝国昔日辉煌。伴随着管弦乐队和唱诗班的庄严而雄伟的合唱，耳边响起桌上黄金落地声和领主们的高谈论阔，让你彷佛置身于遥远的神话国度。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >=夺得胜利或是血洒竞技场=</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220730/extras/4240b52fb467ee0bff09a3b9f8d9cd19.poster.avif?t=1741142009\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220730/extras/4240b52fb467ee0bff09a3b9f8d9cd19.webm?t=1741142009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220730/extras/4240b52fb467ee0bff09a3b9f8d9cd19.mp4?t=1741142009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>召唤强大的生物和英勇的部队，在竞技场上进行战斗。用强大的领主技能践踏你的敌人，你的卡牌将变成无畏的战士，用生命替你而战。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >=策略和运气并存=</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220730/extras/3f7f7d4a95bc9b8b1fb4ebf0556d5a7d.avif?t=1741142009\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>弃牌或者背水一战！每一秒都会成为命运的转折点。考虑好卡牌组合、魔法牌以及领主技能，有策略地下注！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >=耐玩易上手=</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220730/extras/785155358e53e07a88b767b5be96641e.poster.avif?t=1741142009\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220730/extras/785155358e53e07a88b767b5be96641e.webm?t=1741142009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220730/extras/785155358e53e07a88b767b5be96641e.mp4?t=1741142009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>罗凌竞技场的游戏灵感来自于经典的德州扑克玩法，但绝不局限于此。罗凌提供给玩家丰富的角色选择、海量的卡牌和魔法卡，拥有高度的可玩性。即使是新手也会在几轮游戏中掌握游戏机制。",
